sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Requester Client
    participant S as Server Control Plane
    participant B as Target Client
    participant R as Relay or P2P Path

    A->>S: Request remote session
    S->>B: Deliver approval request
    B-->>S: Approve
    S-->>A: Session token and path info
    S-->>B: Session token and path info
    A->>R: Open viewer channel
    B->>R: Open host channel
    A-->>B: Input events
    B-->>A: Screen frames
    A->>S: End session
    S->>B: Finalize and audit
